A '''Class 1 pass''' was a type of security clearance card in the [[New Republic/Legends|New Republic]]. [[Han Solo/Legends|Han Solo]] had wanted to resign his commission, but [[Gial Ackbar/Legends|Ackbar]] pointed out that he would lose these privileges and [[Leia Organa Solo/Legends|Leia]] would lose his council and companionship with Ackbar.

